![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1581558839975-YC31Y4HW7OFRUWDJ1K9W/image-asset.jpeg)

Joker's gone, Batman is nowhere to be found but Harley Quinn and the Birds of Prey are here and they are ready to paint Gotham red. On this episode of the Major Issues Podcast, we dive deep into DC's latest entry into their extended universe, discuss where it may have missed it's mark, and where it sits on the DC sliding scale of quality! Grab your favorite breakfast sandwich, swallow that diamond and get ready to talk the future of Ms. Quinn in this FANTABULOUS episode.  
  
If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBookClique.com**, the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
